settings.comment: Toggle immigration below. It can also be turned on and off through the bot itself. Above list is formatted by user IDs.

distinguishment.comment: Distinguish your most prestigious group members as a little treat for their work in your group. :)

majororganization.comment: This category can be used for any organization you want to majorly recognize. You can only recognize one, so it is suggested to place your current United Nations here.

ranking.comment: You can add as many groups as you want. You can copy and paste the default one, but they should be seperated by commas. You will need to reinput your groupid from above as the main group ID.

ssu.comment: This category allows you to host SSUs for your game using the bot. Copy and paste the below value for as many games as you have, and ensure they are seperated by commas.
ssu.ssuroleid: discord role id for ssu perms
ssu.comment2: The ping should either be @here, @everyone, or a role. Roles should be formatted as '<@&roleid>'. Whatever is put here goes in front of the message.

management.comment: These go by Discord user IDs. Administrators can only be added through the script, so choose wisely.
